data.description: Escape the city & come enjoy the country life. Unique home originally built in Fort Worth Tx, moved to Cleburne TX in 1998. This property sits on 6.661 acres. This property has 2 parcels of land. There is a large workshop that is 20x40 along with a carport for parking along with a pole barn. The home was completely renovated is 2022. Lots of room for a large family. 2 living areas adjacent to an open kitchen and dining area featuring new soft close cabinetry, new SS appliances and gorgeous marble countertops. One of the secondary bedrooms has a private bath, good for a 2nd master. Roof only a little over a year old, Windows installed approx a year ago.
